import React from 'react'
import Navigation from "../Navigation"
// import Footer from "../Footer"
import Header3 from "../All_pages/Header3"
import Advice2 from "../All_pages/Advice2"
import Footer from "../Footer"

const Articles = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Navigation/>
        <Header3/>
        <Advice2/>
        <Footer/>
         
        </>
    )
}

export default Articles
